The following syntax demonstrates how to enable MongoDB Search to index fields
using dynamic and static mappings. To learn more about dynamic and
static mappings, see [dynamic mappings](static-dynamic-mappings).

```json
{
  "mappings": {
    "dynamic": true|false | {
        "typeSet": "<typeset-name>"
    },
    "fields": {
      "<field-name>": {
        "type": "<field-type>",
        ...
      },
      ...
    }
  },
  "typeSets": [
    {
      "name": "<typeset-name>",
      "types": [
        {
          "type": "<field-type>",
          ...
        },
        ...
      ]
    },
    ...
  ]
}
```
